nMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 30, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xeb1665702791582.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xeb1665702791582.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xeb1665702791582.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xeb1665702791582\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Script Editor\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__script_editor_20597\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Script Editor enables you to write ProcScript and JavaScript that controls the behavior of the component.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__p_d5132e1_d5133e1_d5134e1\">The Script Editor contains:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1\">Structure pane—shows the object structure. Use this pane to navigate to objects whose code you want to edit.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2135e1_d2136e1_d2137e1\">Code Editor—enables you to edit ProcScript modules of the selected object.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__p_d5135e1_d5136e1_d5137e1\">It is possible to open a second Script Editor so that you can view and edit the code of two modules or two objects at the same time.</p>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__note_w4050ab1b7b9_w4051ab1b7_w4052ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> By default, the Code Editor shows\n         line numbers, but this can be disabled, which can improve performance when a code container\n         has a large amount of code. See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kqg1746013175741.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kqg1746013175741.html\" title=\"By default, the Script Editor is configured to show line numbers and folding buttons. If you have large amount of code in your code container, you can choose to hide line numbers to improve performance.\">Configure Line Numbering in the Script Editor</a>.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__topic_d2592e1_d2593e1_d2594e1_d2595e1_d2596e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1113083e83\">\n                  \n Shortcut Menu\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Command</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Action</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Insert from Resource Browser</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Inserts the selected snippet into the Script Editor (<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Main editor</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Alternative editor</span>) at the current cursor position.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__note_w4053ab1b7c11b3b3b7b1b3b3_w4054ab1b7c11b3b3b7b1b3_w4055ab1b7c11b3b3b7b1_w4056ab1b7c11b3b3b7_w4057ab1b7c11b3b3_w4058ab1b7c11b3_w4059ab1b7c11_w4060ab1b7_w4061ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The Alternative editor option is available only if the Script Editor has both editing windows open.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Copy</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Copies the selected code to the Clipboard.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xeb1665702791582__table_d467e1_d468e1_d469e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Pastes selected snippet or text from the Clipboard</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__topic_d2597e1_d2598e1_d2599e1_d2600e1_d2601e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1113083e183\">\n                  \n How do I ...\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2138e1_d2139e1_d2140e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ouo1665702763029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ouo1665702763029.html\" title=\"To navigate directly to the script modules of a development object, double-click the object (such as a field, entity, or component) in any worksheet for a modeled entity or component. This opens the Write Script worksheet at the selected object.\">Navigate to ProcScript modules</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2141e1_d2142e1_d2143e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yhf1665702772928.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yhf1665702772928.html\" title=\"You can search for a string or replace a string in the code editor in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu.\">Find and Replace Strings in Code</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2144e1_d2145e1_d2146e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wla1665702773104.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wla1665702773104.html\" title=\"The Write Script worksheet allows you to open two views of the Script Editor, each with its own Structure pane and Code Editor.\">Split Views in the Script Editor</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2147e1_d2148e1_d2149e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nzq1702624284885.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzq1702624284885.html\" title=\"By default, the Script Editor is configured to indent code using a tab character that is equivalent to 4 spaces. If your coding standards or preferences call for the use of spaces or a different tab size, you can change this configuration.\">Configure Indentation in the Script Editor</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qle1665702773192.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qle1665702773192.html\" title=\"Use the Uniface IDE to develop an application, following the Uniface development paradigm of Model, Construct, Build, and Deploy.\">Using the Uniface IDE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__li_d2153e1_d2154e1_d2155e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dkp1665702773261.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dkp1665702773261.html\" title=\"Although development objects can be quite different in content and purpose, the way you create, edit and delete them in the Uniface IDE is essentially the same.\">Working with Development Objects</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__topic_d2602e1_d2603e1_d2604e1_d2605e1_d2606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1113083e255\">\n                  \n Editing\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__p_d5147e1_d5148e1_d5149e1\">You can use <span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+Z</span> and <span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+Y</span> to undo and redo edits. Each editor has its own Undo/Redo stack.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__p_d5150e1_d5151e1_d5152e1\">You can get help with the parameters of ProcScript functions as you enter code. this is automatically displayed when you type the opening parenthesis.</p>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__p_d5153e1_d5154e1_d5155e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__fig_w4045ab1b7c15b7b1_w4046ab1b7c15b7_w4047ab1b7c15_w4048ab1b7_w4049ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Parameter help\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/paramhelpforfunctions.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xeb1665702791582__note_w4062ab1b7c15b9_w4063ab1b7c15_w4064ab1b7_w4065ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This type of help is not yet available for ProcScript statements.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Script Editor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 30, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Script Editor The Script Editor enables you to write ProcScript and JavaScript that controls the behavior of the component. The Script Editor contains: Structure pane—shows the object structure. Use this pane to navigate to objects whose code you want to edit. Code Editor—enables you to edit ProcScript modules of the selected object. It is possible to open a second Script Editor so that you can view and edit the code of two modules or two objects at the same time. Tip: By default, the Code Editor shows line numbers, but this can be disabled, which can improve performance when a code container has a large amount of code. See Configure Line Numbering in the Script Editor . Shortcut Menu Command Action Insert from Resource Browser Inserts the selected snippet into the Script Editor ( Main editor or Alternative editor ) at the current cursor position. Note: The Alternative editor option is available only if the Script Editor has both editing windows open. Copy Copies the selected code to the Clipboard. Paste Pastes selected snippet or text from the Clipboard How do I ... Navigate to ProcScript modules Find and Replace Strings in Code Split Views in the Script Editor Configure Indentation in the Script Editor Using the Uniface IDE Working with Development Objects Editing You can use Ctrl+Z and Ctrl+Y to undo and redo edits. Each editor has its own Undo/Redo stack. You can get help with the parameters of ProcScript functions as you enter code. this is automatically displayed when you type the opening parenthesis. Note: This type of help is not yet available for ProcScript statements. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}